meta {
  name: 02 Organization Endpoints Smoke
  seq: 3
}

docs {
  Smoke 200 GET per /api/organization/* module created in Phase 2 + Phase 4.
  Asserts auth + DomainScopeGuard pass and the controller returns the
  expected ResponseService contract: { success, data | items, ... }.

  All requests use orgAdminToken. To run, the org of orgAdminToken must
  have operating_scope=ORGANIZATION (otherwise inventory/accounting
  endpoints may be empty but should still return 200).
}
